00:01:29.020 --> 00:01:31.850
So please welcome Joe
as he's setting up.

00:01:31.850 --> 00:01:32.700
How are we doing?

00:01:32.700 --> 00:01:33.340
Good?

00:01:33.340 --> 00:01:33.930
JOE KUTCHERA: Perfect.

00:01:33.930 --> 00:01:35.180
RACHEL: Thanks.

